OL,6,FKirkby Lonsdale's beauty 'disguises'
OL,7,Fthe reality of issues that residents
OL,8,Fface day-to-day, that's according to
OL,9,Fone community service user.
OL,11,FKirkby Lonsdale Community Food
OL,12,FCupboard, which started its service
OL,13,Fduring the pandemic, has moved into a
OL,14,Flarger facility to help support the
OL,15,Fdemand across south Cumbria.
OL,17,FRichard Walter, who has recently
OL,18,Fstarted using the food share scheme,
OL,19,Fsays his need for its service 'came
OL,20,Fout of nowhere'.
