OL,6,FHe said: "It's very humbling being
OL,7,Fhere. I'm very grateful that this
OL,8,Fservice is here. It's just a short-
OL,9,Fterm problem for me, I hope. I haven't
OL,10,Fbeen particularly well, and work's a
OL,11,Flittle hard to come by as a result.
OL,13,F"I'm not able to do the work that I
OL,14,Fwas able to do before. You'd think
OL,15,Fthat Kirkby Lonsdale was a nice,
OL,16,Faffluent town with lots of people and
OL,17,Fplenty of wealth. It is. But it
OL,18,Fdoesn't disguise the fact that there
OL,19,Fare people with challenges."
