OL,6,FThe charity believes the summer ahead
OL,7,Fwill be a real problem for families.
OL,8,FGeneral Manager Amanda Gorton, of
OL,9,FKirkby Lonsdale Community Food
OL,10,FCupboard, says most service users are
OL,11,Fin employment.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's just that the cost of
OL,14,Fliving for us here is high. We have
OL,15,Fthe same pot, but we have to make it
OL,16,Fgo further here. The school holidays
OL,17,Fare a real challenge, because there is
OL,18,Fa real lack of childcare. Working
OL,19,Fhours are reduced so that you can look
OL,20,Fafter the children.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
