OL,6,FVolunteer Janet Bradshaw has been
OL,7,Finvolved since its creation in 2020.
OL,8,FShe said: "In the first lockdown, we
OL,9,Frealised that food and isolation were
OL,10,Fthe key problems people were facing.
OL,11,FIf you're stuck at home, seeing a
OL,12,Ffriendly face once or twice a week is
OL,13,Fimportant. So we started that and we
OL,14,Fdelivered initially to 24 houses."
