OL,6,FSpeaking about the situations people
OL,7,Fcoming through the door find
OL,8,Fthemselves in, she added: "Illness,
OL,9,Fself-employed people becoming ill. You
OL,10,Fknow, unexpected bills, washing
OL,11,Fmachine breaks. Suddenly, you've got
OL,12,Fto find the money for that. You either
OL,13,Fput it on your credit card or you
OL,14,Fdon't spend money on food."
